Class PreferencesDlg.DefaultPreferencePanel.Builder

  • java.lang.Object
    • nl.helixsoft.gui.PreferencesDlg.DefaultPreferencePanel.Builder
  • Enclosing class:
    PreferencesDlg.DefaultPreferencePanel

    public static class PreferencesDlg.DefaultPreferencePanel.Builder
extends java.lang.Object
    Helper class to build preference panel, based on a list of preferences and their types. Builds a panel and adds a textfield for a string, checkbox for a boolean, etc.

    You can't instantiate directly. Use dlg.createBuilder
